,'1474873147'),(1600,10523,'_wp_old_slug','why-contemplationawareness-matters-to-change-and-how'),(2952,10523,'_oembed_1e2c9305b57aa8b337a93e6d77744f51','<iframe width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nKdd8RsbKto?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>'),(1602,10523,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1603,458,'_edit_last','1'),(1604,458,'_thumbnail_id','459'),(1605,458,'_genesis_layout','full-width-content'),(1606,458,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1607,458,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1608,9877,'_edit_last','1'),(1609,9877,'_thumbnail_id','9879'),(1610,9877,'al2fb_facebook_excerpt','“If we do not (address the hegemony of Buddhist America), the powerfully persuasive draw of these ancient teachings will be overwhelmed by the deep misalignment racism and oppressions lay bare. But if we do…our collective transmission will be that much more radiant, powerful and true.”'),(1611,9877,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1612,9877,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1613,9900,'_edit_last','1'),(1614,9900,'_wp_old_slug','meditation-on-love'),(1615,9900,'_thumbnail_id','9867'),(1616,9900,'_genesis_layout','full-width-content'),(1617,9900,'_genesis_description','FREE & ONLINE\n\nJoin Lodro Rinzler, Susan Piver, Sokuzan, and angel Kyodo williams, for a half-day virtual retreat. The theme of the retreat is “Meditating on Love.” Each hour will be dedicated to one of the following topics: loving-kindness, compassion, sympathetic joy and equanimity.'),(1618,9900,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1619,9900,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1620,9926,'_edit_last','1'),(1621,9926,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1622,9926,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1623,9929,'_edit_last','1'),(1624,9929,'_thumbnail_id','9930'),(1625,9929,'_wp_old_slug','9929'),(1626,9929,'_genesis_layout','full-width-content'),(1627,9929,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1628,9934,'al2fb_facebook_image_id','9940'),(1629,9934,'_edit_last','1'),(1630,9934,'_thumbnail_id','9940'),(1631,9934,'al2fb_facebook_excerpt','Got a camera, 30 seconds, and a voice? Want yours to be one of many unique voices helping cut through the perceived separation amongst people in our dharma communities?'),(1632,9934,'al2fb_facebook_text','Got a camera, 30 seconds, and a voice? Want yours to be one of many unique voices helping cut through the perceived separation amongst people in our dharma communities?'),(1633,9934,'_genesis_description','Got a camera, 30 seconds, and a voice? Want yours to be one of many unique voices helping cut through the perceived separation amongst people in our dharma communities?'),(1634,9934,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1635,9936,'_edit_last','1'),(1636,9936,'_wp_old_slug','buddhists-to-go-the-white-house'),(1637,9936,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1638,9958,'al2fb_facebook_text','angel is CTZNWELL\'s resident Spiritual Gangster. She kicks off their Mindful Mondays series every Monday in June.'),(1639,9958,'_genesis_layout','full-width-content'),(1640,9958,'_edit_last','1'),(1641,9958,'_thumbnail_id','9959'),(1642,9958,'al2fb_facebook_image_id','9959'),(1643,9958,'_genesis_description','angel is CTZNWELL\'s resident Spiritual Gangster. She kicks off their Mindful Mondays series every Monday in June.'),(1644,9958,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1645,9958,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1646,9964,'_edit_last','1'),(1647,9964,'_thumbnail_id','9965'),(1648,9964,'al2fb_facebook_text','Want to know about Daily Dharma Gathering? Free one-week trial goes live June 15-21!\nangel has enjoyed teaching the DDG because of it\'s wide variety of teachers from many different traditions, backgrounds, lineages and styles. A cornucopia of dharma that brings teaching right to the comfort of your computer screen.'),(1649,9964,'_genesis_description','Want to know about Daily Dharma Gathering? Free one-week trial goes live June 15-21!\n\nangel has enjoyed teaching the DDG because of it\'s wide variety of teachers from many different traditions, backgrounds, lineages and styles. A cornucopia of dharma that brings teaching right to the comfort of your computer screen.\n'),(1650,9964,'_genesis_layout','full-width-content'),(1651,9964,'al2fb_facebook_image_id','9965'),(1652,9964,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1653,9964,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1654,9966,'_oembed_2c03334d8228a89f169cbcd123879149','<iframe width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/jk9SHiDcH1o?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>'),(1655,9966,'_oembed_time_2c03334d8228a89f169cbcd123879149','1474872924'),(1656,9966,'_edit_last','1'),(1657,9966,'_genesis_description','angel leads a meditation joining an ancient instruction w/ modern centering.\r\n4-Line Sit  & Centering Instruction:\r\n1. Sit Upright\r\n2. Ears against the shoulders\r\n3. Nose against the navel\r\n4. Give one FULL outbreath'),(2938,10519,'_edit_lock','1476342436:1'),(1659,9966,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1660,9966,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1661,9972,'_edit_last','1'),(1662,9972,'_oembed_5f795b87f1b5f8752949fcfe0fa881c1','{{unknown}}'),(1663,9972,'_oembed_1a1f49992c0fbb6f10d439d7972838d8','<iframe width=\"500\" height=\"375\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Fd8luWXIrrc?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>'),(1664,9972,'_oembed_time_1a1f49992c0fbb6f10d439d7972838d8','1476342109'),(1665,9972,'_genesis_description','angel Kyodo williams speaks on climate change, connecting the roots of climate change to racism, white-skin privilege and hegemony, and an economic system that demands the degradation of human beings and the planet.'),(2929,9966,'youtube_link','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jk9SHiDcH1o'),(1667,9972,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1668,9981,'_edit_last','1'),(1669,9981,'_genesis_layout','full-width-content'),(1670,9981,'_thumbnail_id','9984'),(1671,9981,'al2fb_facebook_image_id','9984'),(1672,9981,'al2fb_facebook_text','angel talks Beloved Community w/ Tara Brach, PLANETARY w/ Guy Reid & leads a workshop on “Manifesting Dharma Through Presence” @ BuddhaFest. Ali Smith, Sharon Salzberg & Matthieu Ricard will hold conversations. If in DC, it\'s worth being there for!'),(1673,9981,'_genesis_description','From June 11-14, angel joins wisdom teachers and filmmakers for inspiring film, talks, meditation and music.\n\nangel will talk \"Beloved Community\" with Tara Brach, about the film PLANETARY with director Guy Reid and lead an experiential workshop on \"Embodied Life, Liberated Life: Manifesting Dharma Through Presence.\" The weekend event also brings Holistic Life Foundation\'s Ali Smith, Sharon Salzberg and Tibetan translator Matthieu Ricard for conversations.\n\nThey\'ll be commemorating the Dalai Lama\'s 80th birthday and holding a special tribute for Thich Nhat Hanh. If you\'re in the DC area, it\'s definitely worth being there for.'),(1674,9981,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1675,9988,'_edit_last','1'),(1676,9988,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1677,9991,'_oembed_64cb4afaec1dc6b86248594665914c95','{{unknown}}'),(1678,9991,'_edit_last','1'),(1679,9991,'al2fb_facebook_image_id','10044'),(1680,9991,'_genesis_description','September 13, angel will be a featured guest at a retreat focused on bringing balance to the lives of high-performing women\nRev. angel will deliver a keynote at the Women of Impact Life in Balance daylong, a daylong retreat in Oakland that serves to bring self-identified women of all persuasions together for self-care in a world that demands we take it all in. Check out all the Women of Impact Life in Balance daylong retreat has to offer.'),(1681,9991,'_genesis_layout','full-width-content'),(1682,9991,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1683,9993,'_edit_last','1'),(1684,9993,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1685,10455,'_edit_last','1'),(1686,10455,'_thumbnail_id','10449'),(1687,10455,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1688,10461,'_edit_last','1'),(1689,10461,'_thumbnail_id','10449'),(1690,10461,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1691,10461,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1692,10463,'_edit_last','1'),(1693,10463,'_thumbnail_id','10464'),(1694,10463,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1695,10476,'_edit_last','1'),(1696,10476,'_thumbnail_id','10442'),(1697,10476,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1698,10476,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1699,10519,'_oembed_f99a2b9753194e17f4f664fb6fea279f','<iframe width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HZi3L2CmQaA?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>'),(1700,10519,'_edit_last','1'),(1701,10519,'_oembed_time_f99a2b9753194e17f4f664fb6fea279f','1476342427'),(2945,10523,'_edit_lock','1476342942:1'),(1703,10519,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1704,10519,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1705,9999,'_edit_last','1'),(1706,9999,'_oembed_b3157595469b0d1adac31262505e7f88','{{unknown}}'),(1707,9999,'al2fb_facebook_image_id','10000'),(1708,9999,'_genesis_description','Join Rev. angel and Rusia Mohiuddin and let them help you unleash your inner leadership potential in 2016\n\nRev. angel, alongside Universal Partnership\'s Principal Rusia Mohiuddin, regularly co-facilitate Oppression in the Soma in New York, a retreat in which they help attendees become the best they can be by releasing somatic baggage that hinders their leadership potential.\n\nGive us your best email to stay connected, then sign up for #OIS2016 to be the best, liberated you that you can be.'),(1709,9999,'_genesis_layout','full-width-content'),(1710,9999,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1711,10008,'_edit_last','1'),(1712,10008,'al2fb_facebook_image_id','9863'),(1713,10008,'_genesis_description','angel sat down with Omega to discuss how we can lead like spiritual warriors\n\nRev. angel took some time with Omega Institute to discuss the ways we can “transcend the stories we make up in our own minds about ourselves and our shortcomings\" and build a more just society. Read the interview and get timely insights on being an effective leader.\n\n\n\n\"If we’re willing to be complex in our solutions and our willingness to look at things, and not be slave driven by economic imperatives, and slow down and meet each other—we can do this.\"\n\n— Rev. angel Kyodo williams Sensei'),(1714,10008,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1715,10019,'_edit_last','1'),(1716,10019,'_thumbnail_id','9863'),(1717,10019,'_genesis_description','angel explains how threading your anger through love turns anger into a generative, beneficial force\n\nIn this essay with Omega Institute for Holistic Studies, Rev. angel helps us understand that we don\'t have \'personal\' experiences because we\'re all connected, and speaking to that fact will amount to nothing if our actions don\'t reflect our connectedness.\n\n\"We can’t keep going along and saying, we are collective, we’re connected, and then say, but individually they should do X, Y, and Z. You’re not an individual. No one’s an individual. We’re all active in the web of actions, reactions, and experience.\"\n\n— Rev. angel Kyodo williams Sensei'),(1718,10019,'_genesis_layout','full-width-content'),(1719,10019,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1720,10028,'_edit_last','1'),(1721,10028,'_thumbnail_id','9863'),(1722,10028,'_genesis_description','Rev. angel discusses how inner transformation is directly linked to social transformation\n\nIn this interview with Omega Institute, angel talks about how we can access curiosity, courage and vulnerability in our most difficult moments and thus foster the conditions needed to build a just society.\n\n\"The deeper we go into our suffering the more fervent the wish for the well-being of others. We act. We act because our inaction is felt as a participation in that suffering.\"\n\n— Rev. angel Kyodo williams Sensei'),(1723,10028,'_genesis_layout','full-width-content'),(1724,10028,'_is_featured','no'),(1725,10028,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1726,10048,'_edit_last','1'),(1727,10048,'_genesis_layout','full-width-content'),(1728,10048,'_thumbnail_id','9984'),(1729,10048,'al2fb_facebook_text','Rev. angel will be in Amsterdam for Buddhist Film Festival Europe, where she will participate on a panel with the likes of James Doty (Compassion Research Ctr., Stanford U.) and other leaders in compassion - if you\'ll be in Europe in early October, you should check it out!'),(1730,10048,'_genesis_description','From October 2-5, angel will discuss how to bring more compassion into our lives on a panel at BFFE.\n\nRev. angel will be in Amsterdam for Buddhist Film Festival Europe, where she will participate on a panel with the likes of James Doty (Compassion Research Ctr., Stanford U.) and other leaders to speak on how we can encourage greater  compassion by tapping into and honestly witnessing the different realities we face.'),(1731,10048,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1732,10051,'_edit_last','1'),(1733,10051,'_thumbnail_id','9984'),(1734,10051,'al2fb_facebook_text','From November 6-8 in Washington DC, angel will encourage real social connection with others at Mindful Leadership Summit - if in DC from November 6-8, take some time to infuse more mindfulness in your life at Mindful Leadership!'),(1735,10051,'_genesis_description','From November 6-8 in Washington DC, angel will encourage real social connection with others at Mindful Leadership Summit.\n\nJoin Rev.angel at Mindful Leadership Summit, an event dedicated to building leadership skills and connecting with others in the mindfulness movement to encourage real connection and tap into the wisdom inherent in our bodies. She\'ll give a talk titled \"The Hidden Other: When Mindfulness Meets Unconscious Bias\" that\'s sure to hit home given the prevalence of structural racism in the U.S., made obvious by recent killings of black U.S. citizens Sandra Bland and Michael Garner.'),(1736,10051,'_genesis_layout','full-width-content'),(1737,10051,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1738,10060,'_edit_last','1'),(1739,10060,'al2fb_facebook_text','The leading voice on Transformative Change to speak Nov 15 at TEDx Washington Square - not to be missed if in NY this November 15.'),(1740,10060,'_genesis_description','The leading voice on Transformative Change to speak at TEDx Washington Square\n\nRev. angel will give a talk at NYU for TEDx Washington Square, the theme of which will be \"Practicing Change.\" Being asked to speak at a TEDx about practicing change is quite an exciting development for Rev. angel, the pioneering voice of Transformative Change. We will update this page with the talk title and details as the event approaches. If you\'ll be in the NY area, this TEDx is not to be missed.\n\n10/8 UPDATE: event is postponed so organizers can respond to huge public interest and expand venue accommodations.\nWe\'ll post the new date as soon as possible.'),(1741,10060,'_genesis_layout','full-width-content'),(1742,10060,'_thumbnail_id','9984'),(1743,10060,'_is_featured','no'),(1744,10060,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1745,10065,'_edit_last','1'),(1746,10065,'_thumbnail_id','10040'),(1747,10065,'_genesis_description','Miss the Subtle Activism Summit? Still want to bridge your practice with positive change you seek to bring about in the world?\n\nangel and other peacebuilders taught telesummit attendees about the science of subtle activism and how to bolster their activism through mindful practice. As a gift, we\'d like to give you a special highlight of angel\'s session -  check out the telesummit highlights.'),(1748,10065,'_genesis_layout','full-width-content'),(1749,10065,'_is_featured','no'),(1750,10065,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1751,10071,'_edit_last','1'),(1752,10071,'_thumbnail_id','9867'),(1753,10071,'_is_featured','no'),(1754,10071,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1755,10088,'_edit_last','1'),(1756,10088,'_thumbnail_id','9984'),(1757,10088,'_genesis_description','Rev. angel to deliver lecture for beginning students of Buddhism on November 11\n\nangel will give a lecture in Brooklyn Heights at St. Francis College\'s Department of Philosophy and Religious Studies. The talk title is TBD, and we will update this page as the event develops.'),(1758,10088,'_genesis_layout','full-width-content'),(1759,10088,'_is_featured','no'),(1760,10088,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1761,10090,'_edit_last','1'),(1762,10090,'_thumbnail_id','9984'),(1763,10090,'_genesis_description','Rev. angel is a guest at MNDFL meditation center\'s reception, titled \"Love and Justice,\" in NY\n\nThis November, angel is helping kick off the opening of a new meditation center in New York. The brainchild of Lodro Rinzler and Ellie Burrows, MNDFL (pronounced \"mindful\") was created to make space in the chaotic lives of New Yorkers to sit quietly, reset, reflect, and just breathe.'),(1764,10090,'_genesis_layout','full-width-content'),(1765,10090,'_is_featured','no'),(1766,10090,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1767,10264,'_edit_last','1'),(1768,10264,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1769,10266,'_is_featured','no'),(1770,10266,'_edit_last','1'),(1771,10266,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1772,10268,'_edit_last','1'),(1773,10268,'_thumbnail_id','9761'),(1774,10268,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1775,10285,'_is_featured','no'),(1776,10285,'_edit_last','1'),(1777,10285,'_genesis_layout','primary-below-content'),(2922,9972,'_edit_lock','1476341990:1'),(1779,10285,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1780,10287,'_edit_last','1'),(2880,10285,'_edit_lock','1476341860:1'),(1782,10287,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1783,10289,'_edit_last','1'),(1784,10289,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1785,10297,'_edit_last','1'),(1786,10297,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1787,10306,'_is_featured','no'),(1788,10306,'_edit_last','1'),(1789,10306,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1790,10448,'_edit_last','1'),(1791,10448,'_thumbnail_id','10449'),(1792,10448,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(2757,10845,'_EventShowMapLink','1'),(2758,10845,'_EventShowMap','1'),(2755,10631,'_edit_lock','1477375600:1'),(1797,10427,'_edit_last','1'),(1798,10427,'_wp_convertkit_post_meta',''),(1799,10458,'_edit_last','1'),(1800,10458,